@node IML-71 " MSG-71  Subject: Re: Amiga rendering programs"

Subject: Re: Amiga rendering programs
Date: Mon, 8 Aug 94 12:21:05 CDT
From: wilks@lbm.com (Stephen Wilkinson)

torgeir.holm@tbc.powertech.no (Torgeir Holm) replied:

[snip]
> Actually, Real3D 2.49 just came out for Windows about six weeks ago. It
> is virtually identical to the amiga version.
