@node IML-110 " MSG-110  Subject: Star flare texture!"

Subject: Star flare texture!
Date: Wed, 10 Aug 94 17:03:37 +0100
From: milan@valkieser.nl (Milan Polle)

And I'm back with a n-pointed star flare texture.
Use it just like twinkle (on a bright plane that is with the z
axes sticking out of the plane).

You can set outer and inner radius and numer of points, the
radius settings aren't exact, but who cares.

The thing alters transparancy of the plane.

A version with color range and maybe one with y axis sticking out
for easy tracking (why use a flare on the ground) will be comming
as soon as I make them :)

Again grtz, Milan.


