     the Transformation Requester, the Move or Rotate commands, or with the
     Mouse in the Perspective Window. Nor does Redraw update it. 
     
     It can be updated by entering the Transformation Requester, which does 
     indicate the correct values, and hitting Perform.  It can also be 
     updated by leaving and returning to Camera View Mode. This would be a 
     nice one to fix. 
     
