In a message of 13 Aug 94 at 21:31:14 Michael Rivers wrote to me about Escape
Key:

 MR> I've found that pressing the Escape key during updates, will cause the
 MR> update
 MR> to stop, it works after rotations,moves,scales,scrolling and zooming.
 MR> Couldn't
