KellyAnnGothic

SC2
---
Brush-Script-Normal-Italic
Coronet-SemiBold-Italic
Dobkin-Script
Juliet
LaurenScript
NuptialScript
RSAlison

That's it for now... anyone else's experience?
ttyl,
bruce

