> Rend24's "auto" mode where it sits and waits for files to convert, but had no
> 
> luck getting it to work.  Any suggestions?  What's the newest version of
> Rend24?
Yeah, Rend24 has a strange behavior. It's related with the inputting 
parameters. The explanation in manual about the start/end/offset is 
wrong, use them in a intuitive way (what you should think) and the 
program will work flawlessly.

