From: Joop.vandeWege@MEDEW.ENTO.WAU.NL

Hello Kaj,

- Set the number of frames in the action editor to a number higher than 1(10)
- Load OBJECT_1 in frame 1
- Load OBJECT_2 in frame 2 to the (10)
